510
00:39:15,994 --> 00:39:20,994
Are they all terms? Yes, these thugs? And who sponsored them? Mr. Adenauer.

511
00:39:20,994 --> 00:39:25,994
Well, let's leave it. I'm just getting upset, it's no use.

512
00:39:25,994 --> 00:39:30,994
So now you know a lot about me. Sören zu Militär was in your company. Yes.

513
00:39:30,994 --> 00:39:35,862
