515
00:39:40,862 --> 00:39:45,862
The authorization on you? That the Führer signed? Mhm.

516
00:39:45,862 --> 00:39:50,633
Yes, yes, I had it, but I no longer have it. Hmm.

517
00:39:50,633 --> 00:39:55,633
What did you think about it at the time? What should I have thought?

518
00:39:55,633 --> 00:40:00,633
I thought: "Thank God I'm not going to a concentration camp." Mhm. That's clear.

519
00:40:00,633 --> 00:40:05,633
And what was the camaraderie like? Bad. Very bad. Hmm. Very bad.

520
00:40:05,633 --> 00:40:08,457
