521
00:40:08,457 --> 00:40:13,457
Im-- I was in the front line in the trenches in a positional war, so not in combat, uh...

522
00:40:13,457 --> 00:40:18,033
Well, we were in a trench war, in the trenches.

523
00:40:18,033 --> 00:40:23,033
