00:41:11,728 --> 00:41:16,728
They knew very well that we were a Berlin, uh, company, uh, of, uh-- you see

536
00:41:16,728 --> 00:41:21,207
I'm at a loss for words-- of demoted men. Mhm.

537
00:41:21,207 --> 00:41:26,207
And said: "We know you're from Berlin. Come over here to us." Literally.

538
00:41:26,207 --> 00:41:31,207
