557
00:42:54,512 --> 00:42:59,512
(clears throat) The man was immediately recalled to his old rank.

558
00:42:59,512 --> 00:43:04,283
So he immediately became a first lieutenant again

559
00:43:04,283 --> 00:43:09,283
