00:43:13,957 --> 00:43:18,957
He also wanted to become a non-commissioned officer again or whatever.

562
00:43:18,957 --> 00:43:23,957
And he made an attempt to do something over there. Probably didn't get very far.

563
00:43:23,957 --> 00:43:28,436
