564
00:43:28,436 --> 00:43:32,915
And then we heard him screaming day and night.

565
00:43:32,915 --> 00:43:37,915
He'd been shot by the Russians and must have been-- And we gathered that from his...

566
00:43:37,915 --> 00:43:42,915
He screamed for a long time. He must have been shot in the stomach.

567
00:43:42,915 --> 00:43:47,915
And the camaraderie among us was so great that no one even cared about the guy.

568
00:43:47,915 --> 00:43:52,915
We thought: "Oh well, if he does that, it's his own business." Then he bled to death.

569
00:43:52,915 --> 00:43:57,915
We didn't give a damn. Yes? That's how hard it was there.

570
00:43:57,915 --> 00:44:02,915
And that's how good the camaraderie was. And when you became a soldier. Me?

571
00:44:02,915 --> 00:44:05,836
What did you think about that?

572
00:44:05,836 --> 00:44:10,836
Did you think: "That's funny that I was a-" I told you earlier

