00:44:10,836 --> 00:44:15,836
I told you earlier, I was glad I didn't have to go to a concentration camp.

574
00:44:15,836 --> 00:44:19,536
Maybe I'm that cowardly, I don't know.

575
00:44:19,536 --> 00:44:24,536
