586
00:45:12,326 --> 00:45:17,326
in a jungle area. Under the most difficult conditions.

587
00:45:17,326 --> 00:45:22,326
My father only lived there for a few days and, er, was probably bitten by an insect.

588
00:45:22,326 --> 00:45:27,326
He had to be taken to Bahia by motorboat on some river.

589
00:45:27,326 --> 00:45:32,326
