594
00:45:52,326 --> 00:45:56,707
Asselmann Schimero or Matau or and, and, and.

595
00:45:56,707 --> 00:46:01,707
Yes, and now you know all about me. Do you feel Jewish yourself? Uh, no.

596
00:46:01,707 --> 00:46:05,310
I don't have the upbringing for that.

597
00:46:05,310 --> 00:46:10,310
I, it was like this, my brother is three years older and was born before marriage.

598
00:46:10,310 --> 00:46:15,310
And then my Jewish father married my Protestant mother.

599
00:46:15,310 --> 00:46:18,328
And then I was born in wedlock.

600
00:46:18,328 --> 00:46:23,328
And then my father's orthodox Jewish mother tried to have my grandson circumcised.

601
00:46:23,328 --> 00:46:27,905
And my mother fought tooth and nail against it.

602
00:46:27,905 --> 00:46:31,994
And then, of course, there was the divide.

603
00:46:31,994 --> 00:46:36,994
My grandmother never forgave my mother for that. They're Texans.

604
00:46:36,994 --> 00:46:41,994
