619
00:47:45,626 --> 00:47:50,202
My grandmother died, I think at nineteen forty.

620
00:47:50,202 --> 00:47:55,202
The next day, the SS came and picked up my two aunts, who were still living with my mother.

621
00:47:55,202 --> 00:48:00,202
What were your aunts' names? Auntie, well Schindler, of course.

622
00:48:00,202 --> 00:48:05,202
She was unmarried. One aunt was sent to Riga, had to dig her own grave

623
00:48:05,202 --> 00:48:10,202
was shot and the other aunt was sent to Theresienstadt and died there.

624
00:48:10,202 --> 00:48:15,070
