625
00:48:15,070 --> 00:48:20,070
I am, if you like, full of hatred for the whole baggage.

626
00:48:20,070 --> 00:48:25,070
Uh, and therefore also, I tell you, for the masses of the German people.

627
00:48:25,070 --> 00:48:30,070
