628
00:48:30,070 --> 00:48:34,939
And my fear is that perhaps not to the same extent

629
00:48:34,939 --> 00:48:39,939
but that we have now reached a point again where anti-Semitism, racism, er

630
00:48:39,939 --> 00:48:42,568
is raising its cheeky head.

631
00:48:42,568 --> 00:48:47,568
And to an extent that we would never have believed in nineteen forty-five.

632
00:48:47,568 --> 00:48:52,568
It's appalling. And, uh, I deal with these things a lot.

